# Homepage created with HTML5,CSS3 and all the fun Web Stuff

## Install Gulp (global)
```sudo npm install --global gulp ```
If you have not already installed. You need it to run the tasks to cross compile the scss.

## Install Depenencies
 ``` npm install ```
 All dependencies are listed in the package.json file.


## Run Gulp Tasks
``` gulp ```
By default gulp starts two tasks, the scss file watcher and the browser sync task.

## Old File watcher (Not needed, but may work for someone too.)
Start SCSS watcher cmd:
``` sass --watch scss:production/css ```

